    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "Bureau files reflect SAC, Detroit, 3/9/60, advised of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "article (which is attached to Perry's letter of 3/21/60)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "appearing in Detroit Times reflecting Flint, Michigan,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "Resident Agency furnished slides of photographs taken",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "by Perry allegedly showing a saucer-like object",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "silhouetted against the moon. Perry contacted Flint RA",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "3/4/60 advising he had been professional photographer,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "had taken photographs of moon and after developing same",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "noted what appeared to be flying object in one of them.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "Perry furnished information to press. Flint RA",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "received press inquiry, advised only that Perry had",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "turned 2 slides over to FBI and they were being made",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "available to appropriate authorities. Detroit Times",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "advised 3/9/60 FBI has not and is not conducting",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "investigation concerning slides but turned over the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "information to the Air Force. When slides turned over",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "to Air Force, they were requested to return slides to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
